the-beverly-hill-billies.title: The Beverly Hill Billies
the-beverly-hill-billies.description: Beverly Hill Billies is a radio and television crime drama about the cases of a dedicated Los Angeles police detective, Sergeant Joe Friday, and his partners.

episodes.title: Episode 01
episodes.description: Friday and Smith investigate a case where a man threatens to detonate a bomb unless his demands are met.

episodes.title: Episode 02
episodes.description: A series of phone booth robberies leads Friday and Smith to a dangerous criminal ring.

episodes.title: Episode 03
episodes.description: Friday and Smith investigate a case involving stolen fishing equipment and a mysterious boat.

episodes.title: Episode 04
episodes.description: A stolen religious statue leads to a deeper investigation of a local crime ring.

episodes.title: Episode 05
episodes.description: Friday and Smith investigate a series of prison breaks and the mastermind behind them.
